  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His picture was printed in 1905, and forward here in the United States, about his acting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then when he-- after he married my mother-- of course, he became a settled man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had all kinds of different businesses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Are you interested in them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, he was a-- he had a store of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tobacco-- no kind of accessories to tobacco, smoking.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1931, he became a director of a bank, which was a Jewish bank.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the Wall Street Crash, the bank-- the bank when bankrupted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then he was back in a different business also, in selling all kinds of-- I don't know how it would be English word-- women's accessories, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I left home in 19-- one thing, yes, which the reason that I went to Russia is that he wasn't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a war prisoner in the Germans, during the First World War, by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the war broke out with Germany, we decided that we are not going to stay home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are going to out to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it is where I am when the war broke out in 1939.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was ready to go, but then there was the Settlement Pact between Hitler and Stalin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They divided Poland, and now part of Poland became part of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Lutsk was a city of about 25,000, 28,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were maybe 5,000, 7,000 Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had all kind-- all Jewishes which existed at that time in the Jewish world, they existed in our town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All kinds of parties, political parties.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, the only religion that we knew was the Orthodox religion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But here, we can more orthodox or less orthodox, but we didn't have any of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
